  "text": "[Bug] Style variables not working with TSX src import\n\n### Version\r\n\r\n3.1.0-beta.5\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n\r\n[https://github.com/wenfangdu/vue-3-style-vars-tsx-repro](https://github.com/wenfangdu/vue-3-style-vars-tsx-repro)\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nPlease use the repro link.\r\n\r\nThis issue is similar to https://github.com/vuejs/vue-next/issues/3808, but via [src imports](https://vue-loader.vuejs.org/spec.html#src-imports).\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n\r\nWorks with TSX src import\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n\r\nNot working with TSX src import\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
